IZGUBITI TU TVOJU GLAVU.

555
01:00:16,873 --> 01:00:17,671
SHVATI TO.

556
01:00:27,385 --> 01:00:28,335
<FONT COLOR="#C0C0C0">UPOZORENJE</FONT>

557
01:00:40,696 --> 01:00:42,915
